{"tid":580964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老闆性侵女同志　大哥不要啦！","createTime":"2018-03-05T02:36:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T11:42:45.000Z","uid":72009,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c1c2e0a0b8f3fc3ff5c0438e84f252ebcf44f96c","tid":580964,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T02:36:30.000Z","msg":"根據《聯合報》報導，女同志小紋(化名)是某連鎖飲料店的高階主管，負責海外分店業務，主要為黃姓老闆妻的下屬，和黃老闆情同家人。2014年1月與黃老闆與友人、員工到廣東遊玩，入住飯店時小紋因不勝酒力到房間床上休息，黃男竟隨同入內，並強脫褲並性侵小紋得逞，期間小紋不斷反抗大叫「大哥不要啦！」<br />\n小紋事後不堪性侵陰霾，因此提出離職，甚至因此罹患「創傷後壓力症候群」接受心理諮詢，最後受不了報警。黃男在偵訊時否認犯罪，指稱怎麼會找小紋，小紋是「男的」，隨便想也知道不可能。台中地院法官認為小紋遭受身心極大痛苦，也喪失長年努力成果及繼續在高薪公司工作的機會，判黃男3年10月徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180305/1308279\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180305%2F1308279&d=nlrPi3nMy9KbhsAnuhLAXzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=007ff7fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180305%2F1308279&h=c25ce4d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180305/1308279</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b43692e1bda354526536fd552014a760c26e810b","tid":580964,"uid":60787,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T02:38:26.000Z","msg":"男的也好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21bc5296ec2b9b12e71a4549fbd61cccc098bc4d","tid":580964,"uid":38988,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T02:40:53.000Z","msg":"成篇新聞唔會提到警方會點破案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"234c29b269478f2d7ec27a9727b1f2b5667a9685","tid":580964,"uid":7021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T03:01:54.000Z","msg":"等睇果張圖"},{"pid":"55259838a7d33a07938dfe8927e0ccc8e37c3ba7","tid":580964,"uid":78620,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"